description: Details of design and external appearance for Blocks F & G (condition 2) together with areas not covered by buildings (condition 4), refuse (condition 6), public entrances (condition 9), lighting (condition 12), public routes (condition 15) and landscaping (condition 2 & 22)  pursuant to outline planning permission dated 02.01.08 (2006/4533) for the erection of seventeen buildings (including those already built) comprising 1,084 residential dwellings, 36,367 sq.m. of commercial floor space, retail/restaurants/cafés/bars, offices, hotel and leisure and community uses, together with associated car parking and landscaping.
